\v 11 Nak da yo do wadaŇček gen on d…®ma day…®sat. Nak nandak nandak yaŇč naŇč k…®l…® nandako p…®sag…®t: Nak yo kab…®no morapm…® bo morapm…® d…®ma, uŇčun do nandaba k…®k d…®ma asat, k…®si tag…® g…®n yaŇč nand…®sat.
